cle><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/f56370b7da5e03bbc648642da149afc1" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2008/04/100_1873-140x200.jpg" width="70" height="100" alt="Ilaria Grippaudo" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Ilaria Grippaudo"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/ilaria-grippaudo/">View all articles by Ilaria Grippaudo</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2011/03/modena-teatro-comunalemacbeth/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> Modena, Teatro Comunale:&#8221;Macbeth&#8221;</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2011/03/bilbaomacbeth/" rel="next">Bilbao:&#8221;Macbeth&#8221; <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"><div id="respond" class="comment-respond"><h3 id="reply-title" class="comment-reply-title">Lascia un commento <small><a rel="nofollow" id="cancel-comment-reply-link" href="/2011/03/palermo-teatro-massimola-gioconda/#respond" style="display:none;">Annulla risposta</a></small></h3><form action="http: